data.description: This home offers a tranquil setting. As you step inside, the main floor unfolds to reveal a spacious great room, perfect for gatherings, while the formal dining area is ready for your extended table to create memorable dinners. The kitchen is a standout feature, showcasing beautiful cabinets, granite countertops, and a generously-sized walk-in pantry. Large rooms, two master suites (one conveniently on the main level), and two family rooms. Two gas fireplaces add charm and warmth to the living spaces. Upstairs, a well-placed laundry room complements the generous bedrooms, each equipped with walk-in closets. Step outside to a nearby park or enjoy the hot tub for relaxation.
